    <section id="id1170640272671">
      <title>Your own business venture</title>
      <para id="id1170640258602">1. Start your own business</para>
      <para id="id1170639433173">Would you like to be the boss of your own business one day?</para>
      <para id="id1170639089182"><emphasis effect="bold">What do we call a person who recognises a particular </emphasis>need <emphasis effect="bold">or </emphasis>desire<emphasis effect="bold">, gets a </emphasis>bright idea<emphasis effect="bold"> for providing a </emphasis>service<emphasis effect="bold"> or a </emphasis>product<emphasis effect="bold"> and then starts a </emphasis>business<emphasis effect="bold"> to meet that need or desire?</emphasis></para>
      <para id="id1170639460726">An E r.</para>
      <para id="id1170634038167">An entrepreneur therefore converts a need that he or she has identified into a business.</para>
      <para id="id1170642388968">This business can involve <emphasis effect="bold">goods</emphasis> or <emphasis effect="bold">services</emphasis>.</para>
      <para id="id1170640191189">A definition of “goods”</para>
      <para id="id1170634632282">Goods are products that are manufactured and that are for sale.</para>
      <para id="id1170636887236">What is meant by services?</para>
      <para id="id1170639203179">These are particular tasks that are carried out to benefit you and for which you pay.</para>
    </section>
