    <section id="id1170640309700">
      <title>[LO 4.1]</title>
      <list id="id1170640277083" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>To be able to start your own business requires particular personality traits. Let’s try to find out whether you may be an entrepreneur. Answer each of the following questions by indicating <emphasis effect="bold">Yes</emphasis>, <emphasis effect="bold">No</emphasis> or <emphasis effect="bold">Maybe</emphasis> by means of crosses in the appropriate blocks of the questionnaire:</item>
